o px-5 max-w-[1024px] h-14 flex items-center justify-between"><button class="flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-medium tracking-tight hover:opacity-70 font-barlow cursor-pointer" style="transition:opacity 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1), color 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);opacity:1"><img src="/favicon/favicon.svg" alt="" class="w-5 h-5"/>雒艺涵 Luo Yihan</button><div class="flex items-center" style="transition:opacity 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);opacity:1;pointer-events:auto"><a href="/en" class="relative flex items-center h-9 w-[88px] p-[3px] rounded-xl bg-neutral-100 border border-neutral-200 cursor-pointer select-none font-barlow" role="switch" aria-checked="false"><span class="absolute left-[3px] h-[28px] w-[40px] rounded-[8px] bg-white shadow-sm" style="top:calc(50% - 14px);transition:transform 200ms ease-in-out;transform:translateX(40px)"></span><span class="relative z-10 flex-1 text-center text-sm font-medium text-neutral-400" style="transition:color 200ms ease-in-out">EN</span><span class="relative z-10 flex-1 text-center text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900" style="transition:color 200ms ease-in-out">中</span></a></div></div></header><div class="min-h-screen pt-14 animate-page-fade-in"><!--$--><main><div class="mx-auto px-5 max-w-[1024px]"><section class="flex-col md:flex-row flex items-start md:justify-between mt-16 mb-16 md:mb-12"><div class="w-full"><h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight md:pr-8 mb-2">雒艺涵</h1><p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-tight mb-8" style="color:#7C3AED">AI 产品设计师 &amp; <span class="inline-block"><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:0ms">A</span><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:40ms">I</span><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:80ms"> </span><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:120ms">产</span><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:160ms">品</span><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:200ms">设</span><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:240ms">计</span><span class="inline-block animate-letter-bounce" style="animation-delay:280ms">师</span></span></p><div class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4"><p class="mb-4">我是雒艺涵，AI 产品设计师。我的工作横跨 AI 创作、交互设计与用户研究。</p><p class="mb-4">我本科毕业于<a class="underline hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity" href="/zh/experience/artcenter-college-of-design">艺术中心设计学院</a>交互设计专业，研究生毕业于南加州大学交互媒体研究硕士，目前在腾讯音乐工作。</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-4 md:inline-flex md:flex-nowrap gap-3 text-sm"><a class="whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 px-5 py-2 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300" href="/zh/resume">简历</a><a href="mailto:luoyihan17@gmail.com" class="whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 px-5 py-2 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300">邮件</a><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sakura-yihan-luo-a151451b1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 px-5 py-2 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300">领英</a><button class="whitespace-nowrap inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 px-5 py-2 rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer transition-colors duration-300">微信</button></div></div></section><section class="mb-20"><h2 class="mb-6 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight">经历</h2><div class="flex text-base whitespace-nowrap"><div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-white z-10"><div class="h-8 flex items-center pr-2 font-semibold text-neutral-500 border-b"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-wi