nsition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease"/></div><div class="mt-2"><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug group-hover:underline">QQ 音乐 AI 创作</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 line-clamp-2 mt-1">负责AI唱作功能产品定位，核心交互与持续迭代</p></div></a><a class="group block" href="/zh/project/dashboard-concept"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-black/10 aspect-[2/1] md:aspect-[3/2] cover-skeleton"><img src="/assets/personal/project-dashboard.svg" alt="Vemus未音独立APP" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105" style="opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease"/></div><div class="mt-2"><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug group-hover:underline">Vemus未音独立APP</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 line-clamp-2 mt-1">从0到1搭建AI唱作独立APP，探索AI生成音乐的独家体验</p></div></a><a class="group block" href="/zh/project/notes-system"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-black/10 aspect-[2/1] md:aspect-[3/2] cover-skeleton"><img src="/assets/personal/project-notebook.svg" alt="World In A Cell" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105" style="opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease"/></div><div class="mt-2"><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug group-hover:underline">World In A Cell</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 line-clamp-2 mt-1">南加大 VR 细胞生物学教育游戏，主导 VR 交互流程与用户界面设计</p></div></a><a class="group block" href="/zh/project/neoncity"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-black/10 aspect-[2/1] md:aspect-[3/2] cover-skeleton"><img src="/assets/personal/project-lab.svg" alt="NeonCity VR 游戏" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105" style="opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease"/></div><div class="mt-2"><div class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-snug group-ho