"text-neutral-600 text-base whitespace-nowrap text-right"><time dateTime="2021-06-01">2021.06.01</time></span></a></div></section><section class="mb-32"><h2 class="mb-8 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight">创作</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4"><a class="group block" href="/zh/creation/visual-experiment"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-black/10 aspect-[2/1] md:aspect-[3/2] cover-skeleton"><img src="/assets/personal/project-lab.svg" alt="国际机器人与艺术设计双年展" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105" style="opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease"/></div><h3 class="mt-2 text-base font-semibold group-hover:underline">国际机器人与艺术设计双年展</h3><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mt-1"><span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600">Curator</span><span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600">Robotics</span><span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600">Art</span></div></a><a class="group block" href="/zh/creation/prototype"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-black/10 aspect-[2/1] md:aspect-[3/2] cover-skeleton"><img src="/assets/personal/project-dashboard.svg" alt="OMNI Art Expo 全球艺术高校作品联展" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105" style="opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease"/></div><h3 class="mt-2 text-base font-semibold group-hover:underline">OMNI Art Expo 全球艺术高校作品联展</h3><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mt-1"><span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600">Curator</span><span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600">Founder</span><span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-600">Exhibition</span></di